{
  "stem": "24614.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What is she doing?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm also lucky that-- I can count them on one hand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I have a friend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have two friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Gratz College Board, when Danny died, was very supportive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Gratz then didn't have life insurance, didn't have pension fund, didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I remained a poor widow but a rich widow, very rich.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wouldn't change it for millions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was life that's teaching me that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think that our messages and our videos and all of this, if we don't teach people about those things, then we are only telling a story.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't want mine to become a story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I want it to become a lesson.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I want it to become something that people will be able to learn from and say, hey, she could do it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I can do it too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was part of my meeting Danny, living with Danny, and having wonderful days and years with Danny.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, that was very, very-- Danny, in 1962, organized-- Danny used to be in charge, we used to be in charge here of a camp.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Danny bought a Zionist camp in Galil, in Bucks County.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It belongs to the Zionist movement.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It doesn't belong to anybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He went and begged a few rich people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They paid for it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's 60 acres in Doylestown, near Ottsville.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And every summer, there are 200 kids there who are learning about Zionism, Israel, co-operative living, Judaism.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Rabbi Albert Storer goes there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then Danny became president of Gratz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Although, Danny was first a teacher at Gratz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then he was a principal of Gratz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then he was administrator.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then he became president of Gratz.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
